column16: Chris Coghlan flies out to center fielder Mike Aviles.
Kris Bryant hits a grand slam (8) to center field.   Addison Russell scores.    Dexter Fowler scores.    Mike Baxter scores.
Mike Baxter hit by pitch.    David Ross scores.    Addison Russell to 3rd.    Dexter Fowler to 2nd.
Dexter Fowler walks.   David Ross to 3rd.    Addison Russell to 2nd.
Addison Russell singles on a ground ball to left fielder Michael Bourn.   Kyle Schwarber scores.    David Ross to 2nd.
David Ross reaches on a fielding error by shortstop Francisco Lindor.   Chris Coghlan scores.    Kyle Schwarber to 3rd.
